:::Defection looked at the great orb of energy that is the Epiphany:::

"it is time DataStreak." Herald whispered. DataStreak stepped forward his 
chestplate opened to revile his spark the spark floated forward and touched 
the Epiphany. there was a blast of light and the spark returned to 
DataStreak. Data looked different he was bigger and with silver streaks! his 
optics glowed but still didn't work.

DataStreak spoke "We must go to the British isles to find Wisdom."

Jets pooped out of his legs and he took of closely followed by Defection and 
Herald
